text: Michael Dennis Morgan (born December 19, 1946) is an Australian rower, who has competed in the Olympics. He attended Newington College (1957-1965).Newington College Register of Past Students 1863-1998 (Syd, 1999) pp 139 == References == Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Sydney Category:Australian rowers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Australia
